  • Classes 
    Class Description
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.armeria.legacy.LegacyCentralDogmaBuilder
    Use ArmeriaCentralDogmaBuilder.
  • Fields 
    Field Description
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.server.metadata.PerRolePermissions.DEFAULT
    Use PerRolePermissions.ofDefault().
  • Methods 
    Method Description
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.AbstractCentralDogmaBuilder.uri​(String)
    Use AbstractCentralDogmaBuilder.host(String) or AbstractCentralDogmaBuilder.profile(String...).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.fileWatcher​(String, String, Query<T>)
    Use WatcherRequest.start() via CentralDogmaRepository.watcher(Query).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getDiff​(String, String, Revision, Revision, String)
    Use DiffRequest.get(Revision, Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.diff(String).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getDiffs​(String, String, Revision, Revision, String)
    Use DiffRequest.get(Revision, Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.diff(PathPattern).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getFile​(String, String, Revision, String)
    Use FileRequest.get(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.file(String).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getFiles​(String, String, Revision, String)
    Use FilesRequest.get(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.file(PathPattern).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getHistory​(String, String, Revision, Revision)
    Use HistoryRequest.get(Revision, Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.history().
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.getPreviewDiffs​(String, String, Revision, Change<?>...)
    Use PreviewDiffRequest.get(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.diff(Change[]).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.listFiles​(String, String, Revision, String)
    Use FilesRequest.list(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.file(PathPattern).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.mergeFiles​(String, String, Revision, MergeSource...)
    Use MergeRequest.get(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.merge(MergeSource...).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.push​(String, String, Revision, String, Change<?>...)
    Use CommitRequest.push(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.commit(String, Change...).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.repositoryWatcher​(String, String, String)
    Use WatcherRequest.start() via CentralDogmaRepository.watcher(PathPattern).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.watchFile​(String, String, Revision, Query<T>)
    Use WatchRequest.start(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.watch(Query).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma.watchRepository​(String, String, Revision, String)
    Use WatchFilesRequest.start(Revision) via CentralDogmaRepository.watch(PathPattern).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.common.Query.identity​(String)
    Use Query.ofText(String) or Query.ofJson(String).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.common.Revision.minor()
    Do not use. Minor revisions are not used anymore.
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.common.Revision.onMainLane()
    Do not use. Minor revisions are not used anymore.
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.server.CentralDogmaBuilder.cacheSpec​(String)
    Use CentralDogmaBuilder.repositoryCacheSpec(String).
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.server.CentralDogmaConfig.cacheSpec()
    Use CentralDogmaConfig.repositoryCacheSpec().
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.server.storage.repository.Repository.normalize​(Revision)
    Use Repository.normalizeNow(Revision).
  • Constructors 
    Constructor Description
    com.linecorp.centraldogma.common.Revision​(int, int)
    Use Revision(int) instead. Minor revisions are not used anymore.
